channel.title: [New-Reality] Needs 1 developer.. Project almost done RE:
channel.description:
Hi, ive been working on new reality for a while now.. BUT NOW IM LOOKING FOR SOME DEVELOPING HELP.. -the original source I got had already had a years of work into it.. Right now new-reality has almost perfected combat.. We are now just working on small things to finish up the server and make it the ultimate experience.. Right now we have 2 developers myself and 1 other person (looking for 1 other developer)
-We have domain+ddosed protected web host + ddosed protected vps+ auto vote already with a professional site
-IF you interested in joining the development team send me a message on Skype @ new.realtyrsps
